Thanks
******

   Thanks to all those who suffered through the bugs in various early
versions of IceOLR, your testing is much appreciated.

   Last but not least, thanks to Marrieta for putting up with all the
time I spend on IceBBS development, and for baking all those cookies for
Developers' meetings.


@EndNode

